title: iPhone/iPod Touch Jailbreak, Unlocker, Activator and Installer a
description:
ZiPhone is a program that both jailbreaks, unlocks and activates your iPhone 1.1.4 (jailbreak is also supported for iPod Touch) inonly one click! Its the easiest simplest program that does all you need in only one click. The program also supports advance functions such as fake IMEI and Wi-Fi fix. You can also set your iPhone/iPod Touchin DFU mode which enables you to install whatever firmware you want on your device.

An installer application will also be installed on your device which will enable you to download and install programs/games/video/wallpaper and much more directly to your iPhone/iPod Touch without any need of a computer!

This download contains both Windows and Mac version.



Happy Jailbreaking! ;)
